 HOMEPAGE="http://lct.sourceforge.net"
      REQ="linuxdoc-tools"
    SHORT="console-tools enables the configuration of Linux consoles."
cat << EOF
The console-tools package allows you to set-up and manipulate the Linux
console (ie. text screen and keyboard), and manipulate console-font
files. It was developed from version 0.94 of the standard kbd package,
and integrates many fixes and enhancements, including new kbd features
up to 0.99.
EOF
